title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race Season 8 - Episode 9
description:
Bob and Monét review Drag Race Season 8 Episode 9 and no one's safe as the remaining four queens square off for their final challenge: starring in the music video for Ru's hit single "The Realness."
See Monét and Bob on tour this summer by going to bobandmonet.com !!
